{"tid":1787132,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"分享太空倉計算","createTime":"2019-12-17T16:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T12:50:00.000Z","uid":90323,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"036330f43616469e29551f3c11a8004bb92b8089","tid":1787132,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"(2300月租， 包飯包清潔的太空倉， 業主可月入3萬？) <br />\n<br />\n自已造就這願景很遙遠， 但我希望做出數字讓香港的業主看。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據真積圖探計劃：<br />\n<br />\n1間屋， 約500尺， 3房， 1廳。<br />\n<br />\n租13000-14500<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起2幅牆間5房， 坐廁變2個(空間 800x800) ， 浴缸旁間1個尿兜,   廚房去水增加2個企缸 (800x800) 作為女廁。(樓下有公共澡堂同廁所) <br />\n<br />\n5 房， 每間4500, 22500hkd<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每間房淘寶3-6 個太空倉， (當4個)<br />\n<br />\n5*4*2300(一個倉)  = 46000<br />\n<br />\n花 8000 per person 請2個讀書嘅人返6日，每日5個鐘( 即60元1小時包飯),  負責煮飯洗3 清潔同揾客。<br />\n<br />\n1間屋做到月袋3萬？"},{"pid":"b0192712d13aa3b4fee72a6e53664c20a6e544fb","tid":1787132,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一屆「和你影」攝影比賽 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786771</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3981bb6422f11742c3c1718e44d362067220a2e","tid":1787132,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 - 支援手足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=54d30a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h